Package nl.strohalm.cyclos.access

Interface Summary
AdminPermission Interface implemented by the various administrator permission enumerations
Permission Permissions can be of two types: LIST or BOOLEAN.
PermissionCheck Used to check for permissions according to the logged user.
 

Enum Summary
AdminAdminPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the ADMIN_ADMIN module type
AdminMemberPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the ADMIN_MEMBER module type
AdminSystemPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the ADMIN_SYSTEM module type
BasicPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the BASIC module type
BrokerPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the BROKER module type
MemberPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the MEMBER module type
Module This enum contains all modules defined in Cyclos
ModuleType  
OperatorPermission This enum contains all permissions related to the OPERATOR module type
